Press Alt + Q and search for Purchase Requests. Press New and fill in the requested fields (Number, Description, Vendor):

<a href="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000540-0/3Purchaserequest_ENU.png" target="_blank"><img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000540-0/3Purchaserequest_ENU.png"></a><br>

Main fields:

