<br>

The goods / services for which the Purchase Request is made must be specified in the lines. You can, if necessary, specify dimensions such as Project Code, Department Code, Location Code.

<img width="20" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000540-0/exclamation.png"> **NB**

It is also possible to enter purely descriptive purchase requests if you do not know the Item code and / or Vendor name
You can change the Type and Nr. without altering other information already in the line: From Functions -> Change Type / Nr.

